- Create your lifelike avatar in just a matter of seconds by uploading a selfie\n\nComing Soon:\n- Explore a variety of cultural experiences such as museums, art exhibitions, and more", "short_description": "Welcome to Nostraverse.\n\nHere at Nostraverse, we offer companies a virtual presence in the Metaverse.\n\nStay Connected:\n- Have your own space\n- Meet up with your colleagues\n- Create digital twins of real-life spaces\n\nBe Yourself:\n- Create your lifelike avatar in just a matter of seconds by uploading a selfie\n\nComing Soon:\n- Explore a variety of cultural experiences such as museums, art exhibitions, and more"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://nostraverse.com/flint/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://nostraverse.com/flint/legal", "publisher_name": "Nostraverse", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.nostraverse.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1063584910766706"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["PRODUCTIVITY", "SIMULATION", "UTILITY"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1034458094099304"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "905254094201144"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "905254094201144"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1659423600, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "905254094201144"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary"